<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<script>var vendorSubmitted = false;</script>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Submit Your Audit Data — Optima Workflows</title>
<meta name="description" content="Submit your invoice and receiving records to start your free vendor overbilling audit. Data flows directly into our audit system.">

<style>
:root{
  --bg-dark:#030712; --card-bg-gradient:linear-gradient(145deg,#0b0f19,#060a13);
  --border-color:#1f2937; --text-main:#ffffff; --text-muted:#94a3b8;
  --accent-blue:#38bdf8; --accent-green:#34d399; --accent-rust:#fb923c;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
body{background:var(--bg-dark)!important;color:var(--text-main)!important;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,sans-serif;line-height:1.55;padding-bottom:60px;}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){*{animation:none!important;transition:none!important;}}
.container{max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px;}

.banner{background:#111827;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-color);color:#e0e7ff;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-align:center;padding:10px 12px;letter-spacing:.05em;font-family:monospace;text-transform:uppercase;}
nav{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:22px 24px;}
.logo{font-weight:800;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:-.02em;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;text-transform:uppercase;}
.logo-dot{height:8px;width:8px;background:var(--accent-blue);border-radius:50%;}
.back-link{color:var(--text-muted);font-size:12.5px;text-decoration:none;}
.back-link:hover{color:var(--text-main);}

header{text-align:center;padding:44px 24px 20px;max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;}
.badge{display:inline-block;padding:9px 18px;border-radius:9999px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:22px;letter-spacing:.02em;background:rgba(56,189,248,.1);border:1px solid rgba(56,189,248,.3);color:var(--accent-blue);}
h1{font-size:36px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.18;margin-bottom:18px;}
.gradient-text{background:linear-gradient(to right,#38bdf8,#3b82f6,#ec4899);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;}
.lead{font-size:15px;color:var(--text-muted);max-width:580px;margin:0 auto;}

section{padding:40px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--border-color);}
section:first-of-type{border-top:none;}
.section-title{text-align:center;margin-bottom:26px;}
.section-title h2{font-size:22px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px;}
.section-title p{color:var(--text-muted);font-size:14px;max-width:520px;margin:0 auto;}

.steps{counter-reset:step;margin-bottom:8px;}
.step{display:grid;grid-template-columns:40px 1fr;gap:16px;padding:18px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--border-color);}
.step:last-child{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-color);}
.step-num{counter-increment:step;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:var(--accent-blue);font-family:monospace;}
.step-num::before{content:counter(step,decimal-leading-zero);}
.step h3{font-size:14.5px;margin-bottom:4px;}
.step p{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);}
.step a{color:var(--accent-blue);}

.form-card{background:var(--card-bg-gradient);border:1px solid var(--border-color);border-radius:12px;padding:36px;}
.form-group{margin-bottom:20px;}
label{display:block;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:8px;}
input,textarea,select{width:100%;background:#020617;border:1px solid var(--border-color);border-radius:6px;padding:13px;color:#fff;font-family:inherit;font-size:14px;}
input:focus,textarea:focus,select:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--accent-blue);}
.form-hint{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:6px;}
.consent{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);margin:22px 0;}
.consent input{width:auto;margin-top:3px;}
.submit-btn{width:100%;background:var(--accent-blue);color:#020617;padding:15px;border:none;border-radius:6px;font-weight:800;font-size:14.5px;cursor:pointer;}
.submit-btn:hover{background:#7dd3fc;}

.data-note{background:rgba(52,211,153,.06);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.25);border-radius:10px;padding:18px 22px;font-size:13.5px;color:#d1fae5;margin-top:8px;}
.data-note strong{color:#fff;}

.thank-you-card{background:var(--card-bg-gradient);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.35);border-radius:12px;padding:48px 36px;text-align:center;}
.thank-you-icon{width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(52,211,153,.15);border:1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.4);color:var(--accent-green);font-size:26px;font-weight:800;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 20px;}
.thank-you-card h3{font-size:20px;margin-bottom:12px;color:#fff;}
.thank-you-card p{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);max-width:440px;margin:0 auto;}

footer{text-align:center;padding:36px 0 0;}
footer p{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;}
footer .sig{font-family:monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:18px;padding-top:18px;border-top:1px solid var(--border-color);}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="banner">DATA SUBMITTED HERE FEEDS DIRECTLY INTO YOUR AUDIT · NO MANUAL WAIT</div>

<nav>
  <div class="logo"><span class="logo-dot"></span> OPTIMA WORKFLOWS</div>
  <a href="../vendor-audit/" class="back-link">← Back to Vendor Audit</a>
</nav>

<header>
  <div class="badge">Data Intake · Vendor & Invoice Audit</div>
  <h1>Send Us the Files, <span class="gradient-text">We Start Auditing Immediately</span></h1>
  <p class="lead">Fill in the details below and share your invoice and receiving records. The moment your data lands, it's queued for reconciliation — no back-and-forth needed to get started.</p>
</header>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>Before You Submit</h2>
      <p>Two things make this fast on both ends.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num"></div>
        <div>
          <h3>Export your records as CSV or Excel</h3>
          <p>Vendor invoices, purchase orders, and receiving/goods-received logs for the period you want audited — most ERP and accounting systems export these directly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num"></div>
        <div>
          <h3>Upload to a shared folder and paste the link below</h3>
          <p>Create a folder in Google Drive (or Dropbox/OneDrive), set sharing to "anyone with the link can view," and paste that link into the form. This keeps your files off email entirely.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="intake-form">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>Submit Your Data</h2>
    </div>
    <div id="formWrap" class="form-card">
      <!-- Entry IDs confirmed against Google Form's FB_PUBLIC_LOAD_DATA_ -->
      <form id="intakeForm" action="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScgO72gyxy7BK4BzuoQhFuZz9L9aCGPR7Z6DWJPyr2Wot7Yow/formResponse"
            method="POST" target="hidden_iframe_vendor" onsubmit="vendorSubmitted=true;">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="company">Company Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="company" name="entry.1348135732" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="contact">Your Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="contact" name="entry.217114763" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="entry.1094296420" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="erp">ERP / Accounting System</label>
          <input type="text" id="erp" name="entry.1002308826" placeholder="e.g., QuickBooks, NetSuite, SAP" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="period">Audit Period</label>
          <input type="text" id="period" name="entry.465617798" placeholder="e.g., May 1 – June 30, 2026" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="filelink">Link to Your Files (Drive / Dropbox / OneDrive)</label>
          <input type="text" id="filelink" name="entry.850891188" placeholder="https://drive.google.com/..." required>
          <div class="form-hint">Set sharing to "anyone with the link can view" before pasting it here.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="notes">Anything We Should Know</label>
          <textarea id="notes" name="entry.1335054863" rows="3" placeholder="Known problem vendors, formatting quirks, anything else useful..."></textarea>
        </div>

        <label class="consent">
          <input type="checkbox" name="entry.950697927" value="Please check to proceed" required>
          I confirm I have the right to share this data and understand it will be used only to run this audit.
        </label>

        <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Submit My Data</button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div id="thankYou" class="thank-you-card" style="display:none;">
      <div class="thank-you-icon">✓</div>
      <h3>Got it — your data is in the queue.</h3>
      <p>Reconciliation begins from here. You'll hear from us with findings — or confirmation that nothing recoverable was found — within a few business days.</p>
    </div>

    <iframe name="hidden_iframe_vendor" id="hidden_iframe_vendor" style="display:none;"
            onload="if(vendorSubmitted){document.getElementById('formWrap').style.display='none';document.getElementById('thankYou').style.display='block';window.scrollTo({top:document.getElementById('thankYou').offsetTop-100,behavior:'smooth'});}"></iframe>

    <div class="data-note"><strong>What happens next:</strong> your submission is logged the moment you hit submit, and reconciliation begins from there. You'll hear from us with findings — or confirmation that nothing recoverable was found — within a few business days.</div>
  </div>
</section>


<footer>
  <div class="container">
    <p>Questions before you submit? Reply to the audit-intake email we sent you, or reach out directly — happy to walk through file formatting first if that's easier.</p>
    <div class="sig">Optima Workflows · Vendor Audit Data Intake · Used only for the audit requested.</div>
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
